# Netlify-style routing rules. Lovable publish + Netlify + Cloudflare Pages
# all honor this file. Order matters: more specific rules first.
#
# CRITICAL: We MUST try the prerendered per-route file before falling back to
# the SPA index.html. Without this, every route gets the homepage HTML and
# the entire site canonicals to "/" for crawlers (catastrophic SEO).
#
# Netlify automatically serves static files in dist/ before applying rewrites,
# so dist/ai-checker/index.html is served for /ai-checker. The catch-all below
# is ONLY for client-side routes the prerender list missed (deep blog post
# URLs not yet in prerender-routes.ts, dynamic /help-article/* slugs, etc.).

# Force https + apex domain (one canonical host)
https://aifreetextpro.lovable.app/*  https://aifreetextpro.com/:splat  301!
https://www.aifreetextpro.com/*      https://aifreetextpro.com/:splat  301!

# Tool pages live on the app subdomain — real 301s (the client-side
# ExternalSEORedirect components in App.tsx remain only as a fallback for
# hosts that ignore this file).
/humanizer   https://app.aifreetextpro.com/humanizer   301
/detector    https://app.aifreetextpro.com/detector    301
/auth        https://app.aifreetextpro.com/auth        301
/plagiarism  https://app.aifreetextpro.com/plagiarism  301

# Legacy blog slugs — real 301s (client-side SEORedirect components remain
# as fallback). Meta-refresh stubs pass less link equity than true 301s.
/blog/make-chatgpt-undetectable-guide-2025         /blog/make-chatgpt-undetectable-2025       301
/blog/ai-detection-patterns-perplexity-burstiness  /blog/ai-detection-patterns-explained      301
/blog/academic-ai-writing-thesis-essays-safely     /blog/academic-ai-writing-safely           301
/blog/ai-content-seo-undetectable-articles         /blog/ai-content-seo-undetectable          301
/blog/ai-content-seo                               /blog/ai-content-seo-undetectable          301
/blog/gptinf-vs-ai-free-text-pro-comparison        /blog/gptinf-vs-ai-free-text-pro           301
/blog/originality-ai-review-pricing-bypass         /blog/originality-ai-review-how-to-beat    301
/blog/paraphrasing-vs-humanizing-ai-text           /blog/paraphrasing-vs-humanizing           301
/bypass-turnitin                                   /bypass-turnitin-ai-detection              301

# SPA fallback — runs LAST, only when no static file matched
